<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Where the journey time of eight hours laid down in Chapter VII(2) of the Annex to Directive 91/628/EEC is exceeded, road vehicles used for the transportation of domestic solipeds and animals of the bovine, ovine, caprine and porcine species within the Community must comply with the additional requirements set out in the Annex to this Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui direktiivi 91/628/EM&Uuml; lisa VII peat&uuml;ki l&otilde;ikega 2 s&auml;testatud veo kestus &uuml;letab kaheksat tundi, peavad koduloomadena peetavate kabjaliste, veiste, lammaste, kitsede ja sigade &uuml;hendusesisesteks vedudeks kasutatavad maantees&otilde;idukid vastama k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas etten&auml;htud t&auml;iendavatele normidele. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> By 31 December 2003 at the latest, the Commission shall submit to the Council a report drawn up on the basis of the opinion of the Scientific Veterinary Committee on the implementation of this Regulation and more particularly on the application of the different ventilation systems, together with any appropriate proposals which take account of the conclusions of that report. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjon esitab n&otilde;ukogule hiljemalt 31. detsembriks 2003 veterinaaria teaduskomitee arvamuse p&otilde;hjal koostatud aruande k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse rakendamise kohta, eelk&otilde;ige eri ventilatsioonis&uuml;steemide kohaldamise osas, koos k&otilde;igi nimetatud aruande j&auml;reldusi arvessev&otilde;tvate asjakohaste ettepanekutega </eesti>
<inglise> The Council shall act by a qualified majority on these proposals no later than six months after their submission. </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu teeb nende ettepanekute kohta otsuse kvalifitseeritud h&auml;&auml;lteenamusega hiljemalt kuue kuu jooksul alates ettepanekute esitamisest. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
